ai_flow.util.json_utils module¶

Utilities to dump and load Jsonable object to/from JSONs.

class ai_flow.util.json_utils.Jsonable[source]¶

Bases: object

Base class for serializing and deserializing objects to/from JSON.

The default implementation assumes that the subclass can be restored by updating self.__dict__ without invoking self.__init__ function.. If the subclass cannot hold the assumption, it should override to_json_dict and from_json_dict to customize the implementation.
